    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** Then, a dependent diagram E over D is just a diagram over \u222bD. *)\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition DDiagram {G : Graph} (D : Diagram G)\n  := Diagram (integral D).",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
